<h4>2.2. Repository</h4>

<p>JPA와 연결되는 Repository를 생성한다.</p>

<div class="language-java highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="kn">package</span> <span class="nn">com.exercise.marketplace.user.repository</span><span class="o">;</span>

<span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">com.exercise.marketplace.user.model.UserInfo</span><span class="o">;</span>
<span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository</span><span class="o">;</span>

<span class="kd">public</span> <span class="kd">interface</span> <span class="nc">UserRepository</span> <span class="kd">extends</span> <span class="nc">JpaRepository</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="nc">UserInfo</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="nc">Long</span><span class="o">&gt;</span> <span class="o">{</span>
  <span class="err">#</span> <span class="nc">Long</span> <span class="n">타입의</span> <span class="nc">ID를</span> <span class="n">기반으로</span> <span class="n">위에서</span> <span class="n">생성한</span> <span class="nc">UserInfo</span> <span class="n">클래스에</span> <span class="n">맞는</span> <span class="n">엔티티를</span> <span class="n">반환한다</span><span class="o">.</span>
  <span class="err">#</span> <span class="kd">interface</span> <span class="nc">형태로</span> <span class="nc">JpaRepository를</span> <span class="n">상속하기</span> <span class="n">때문에</span>
  <span class="err">#</span> <span class="no">ID</span> <span class="n">기반의</span> <span class="n">등록</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="n">조회</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="n">삭제</span> <span class="n">등</span> <span class="n">기본적인</span> <span class="n">기능들이</span> <span class="n">자동으로</span> <span class="n">제공된다</span><span class="o">.</span>
<span class="o">}</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

